descript.abstract: Elementary school districts for the Commonwealth of Massachusetts. The district boundaries were created from a database provided by the Massachusetts Department of Education. This database contained the name of each municipality, the name of the elementary, middle, and high school district with which each municipality was associated, and its unique municipal ID. This and associated information (e.g., start and end grade) were joined to a multi-part shape file representing the municipal boundaries. The join was on municipal ID. The districts were created by dissolving municipal boundaries on elementary district ID.

overview.dsoverv: The data set contains the boundaries of elementary school districts in Massachusetts. The districts were created by disolving the boundaries of the MassGIS municipal data layer on the name of the elementary district with which each municipality was affiliated.

srcinfo.srccontr: See the "Abstract" section of this document for details.

procstep.procdesc: The district boundaries were created from a database provided by the Massachusetts Department of Education. This database contained the name of each municipality, the name of the elementary, middle, and high school district with which each municipality was associated, and its unique municipal ID. This and associated information (e.g., start and end grade) were joined to a multi-part shape file representing the municipal boundaries. The join was on municipal ID. The districts were created by dissolving municipal boundaries on the relevant (elementary, middle, high school) district ID.

dataqual.logic: Polygons representing each district arc closed and do not overlap any other district; there are no gaps between district polygons. All districts occur within the bounding polygon of the Commonwealth of Massachusetts.
dataqual.complete: All elementary school districts in Massachusetts are represented, as confirmed by the Mass. Department of Education.

attracc.attraccr: Attributes are complete and were provided by the Massachusetts Department of Education

horizpa.horizpar: Boundaries derived from those used for Massachusetts Municipalities. These were in turn created from boundaries depicted on the 1:25,000 scale USGS quads for Massachusetts. See http://www.mass.gov/mgis/towns.htm for more information on this version of the municipal boundary data layer.
